description: Two pictures stood out in either camp and may indicate who wins on March 10. One was the Prime Minister Narendra Modi’s two-day campaign in Varanasi that seems to have soothed the nerves of many in the BJP camp over the mood in Purvanchal. In the SP’s camp, the big crowds at Akhilesh Yadav’s rallies and road shows is reflective of the confidence and enthusiasm on his side of the results.
